{"id":377778,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/【图说天朝】转眼版眼保健操/","date":"2015-01-11T11:17:19Z","modified":"2015-01-11T10:59:03Z","title":"【图说天朝】“转眼”版眼保健操","content":"<p>该校德育处谭超老师告诉记者，考虑到手部卫生问题、学生难找正确穴位，本学期学校改用一套更为卫生和安全的眼保健操。</p>\n<p>据校方，这是一种名为“多维视觉训练”的眼部体操运动，做操人通过转动眼珠，提高眼肌的兴奋度，增强大脑神经的传导功能，可达到改善近视的效果。</p>\n<p>目前，全校学生都做这套眼保健操，每天两次。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-377799\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1.jpg\" alt=\"新版眼保健操1\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1.jpg 567w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操1-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-377800\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2.jpg\" alt=\"新版眼保健操2\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2.jpg 566w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操2-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-377801\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/新版眼保健操3.jpg\" alt=\"新版眼保健操3\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2